Package valerioFarriciello.View

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddTab
    Class responsible to get the values for players and managers assignments
    CreateTab
    Class responsible to get the values for the creation of players, managers and teams
    DeleteTab
    Class responsible to get the values for the deletion of players, managers and teams
    DisplayTab
    Class responsible to display the values received from the controller
    Main
    The Main class is responsible to group all the GUI components and getting input from the user.
    This class is not responsible for data manipulation or storage.
    ModifyTab
    Class responsible to get the values for the modification of players and managers attributes
    OtherTab
    Simple class that is responsible to show the memory usage (by temporary overloading the memory) and close the connection
    with the database
    RemoveTab
    Class responsible to get the values for removing players and managers from a team
